                          VISION, MISSION, and GOAL

   Our Vision is secure and effective operations for all National Security
   Mission activities.

   Our Mission is to promote and maintain OPSEC principles worldwide by
   assisting our customers in establishing OPSEC programs, providing OPSEC
   training and conducting OPSEC surveys.

   Our Goal is to be recognized as the leader and preferred provider of
   value-added OPSEC products and services.


                       Last Updated on August 6, 2001
